{"tid":491430,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"6名香港少女參選日本AKB48官方姊妹團 TPE48","createTime":"2017-12-06T13:39:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T22:31:40.000Z","uid":53379,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2801c179605b4774d23d22d275cd1303b4bd1ed1","tid":491430,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T13:39:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">6名香港少女參選日本AKB48官方姊妹團 TPE48</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n號稱日系鄰家偶像嘅TPE48，喺日本女子天團AKB48官方公認嘅海外姊妹團，組合名字「TPE」取材自「TaiPei 台北」，而Logo顏色就來自台灣嘅代表性水果「芒果」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.likejapan.com/v2/d//2017/12/editors/9157/20171205164114_5a265baa65ddc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.likejapan.com%2Fv2%2Fd%2F%2F2017%2F12%2Feditors%2F9157%2F20171205164114_5a265baa65ddc.jpg&h=4d3a9c83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTPE48一期生正式招募計劃<br />\n其實管理AKB48嘅製作人 秋原康，早喺2011年已經首次公開過TPE48計劃，可惜事隔一年後，官方宣佈計劃順延。直至2017年7月，官方透過《AKB48 Fan Meeting in TAIWAN》緊急宣佈9月1日正式展開TPE48第一期生嘅徵選活動，當中AKB48 Team K嘅成員，阿部瑪利亞更加會移籍至TPE48!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.likejapan.com/v2/d//2017/12/editors/9157/20171205182601_5a26743986944.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.likejapan.com%2Fv2%2Fd%2F%2F2017%2F12%2Feditors%2F9157%2F20171205182601_5a26743986944.jpg&h=0253d78a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢哋計劃招募40人做第一期生，主要根據官方審查同粉絲投票嘅結果決定。徵選喺10月上旬正式開始，總共有四次審查，暫時去到第三次嘅審查階段。當中有6名香港少女參選，佢哋都順利入到第三次審查，呢6名少女分別喺冼迪琦、林裕君、陳盈臻、馮子敏、劉曉晴、陳嘉希。佢哋除左都喜歡唱歌跳舞之外，亦因為都好仰慕AKB48，希望加入其中成為海外姊妹團成員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.likejapan.com/v2/d//2017/12/editors/9157/20171205192431_5a2681ef26919.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.likejapan.com%2Fv2%2Fd%2F%2F2017%2F12%2Feditors%2F9157%2F20171205192431_5a2681ef26919.jpg&h=3d6b870e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTPE48 香港參賽者<br />\n<br />\n以下係6名香港少女嘅官方簡介，click入去睇吓，支持吓喇!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.likejapan.com/v2/d//2017/12/editors/9157/20171205171015_5a2662779890d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.likejapan.com%2Fv2%2Fd%2F%2F2017%2F12%2Feditors%2F9157%2F20171205171015_5a2662779890d.jpg&h=637a1fac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNo.049 劉曉晴 官方簡介<a href=\"http://www.tpe48.tw/auditionPersonal.html?gid=49\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tpe48.tw%2FauditionPersonal.html%3Fgid%3D49&d=7SLwcdWVY8Mpy4yKxH5Fd9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=f45cd197\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tpe48.tw/auditionPersonal.html?gid=49</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.likejapan.com/v2/d//2017/12/editors/9157/20171205164346_5a265c422b497.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.likejapan.com%2Fv2%2Fd%2F%2F2017%2F12%2Feditors%2F9157%2F20171205164346_5a265c422b497.jpg&h=368bd961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNo.062 冼迪琦 官方簡介<a href=\"http://www.tpe48.tw/auditionPersonal.html?gid=62\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tpe48.tw%2FauditionPersonal.html%3Fgid%3D62&d=7SLwcdWVY8Mpy4yKxH5Fd9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=cc31fe5e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tpe48.tw/auditionPersonal.html?gid=62</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.likejapan.com/v2/d//2017/12/editors/9157/20171205171109_5a2662ad3bf8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.likejapan.com%2Fv2%2Fd%2F%2F2017%2F12%2Feditors%2F9157%2F20171205171109_5a2662ad3bf8c.jpg&h=7e63e5ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNo.063 陳嘉希 官方簡介<a href=\"http://www.tpe48.tw/auditionPersonal.html?gid=63\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tpe48.tw%2FauditionPersonal.html%3Fgid%3D63&d=7SLwcdWVY8Mpy4yKxH5Fd9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=4369d14d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tpe48.tw/auditionPersonal.html?gid=63</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.likejapan.com/v2/d//2017/12/editors/9157/20171205171127_5a2662bf52448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.likejapan.com%2Fv2%2Fd%2F%2F2017%2F12%2Feditors%2F9157%2F20171205171127_5a2662bf52448.jpg&h=8060e802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNo.102 陳盈臻 官方簡介<a href=\"http://www.tpe48.tw/auditionPersonal.html?gid=102\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tpe48.tw%2FauditionPersonal.html%3Fgid%3D102&d=7SLwcdWVY8Mpy4yKxH5Fd9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=c4bf5364\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tpe48.tw/auditionPersonal.html?gid=102</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.likejapan.com/v2/d//2017/12/editors/9157/20171205171144_5a2662d0739e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.likejapan.com%2Fv2%2Fd%2F%2F2017%2F12%2Feditors%2F9157%2F20171205171144_5a2662d0739e2.jpg&h=29dd1730&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNo.116 馮子敏 官方簡介<a href=\"http://www.tpe48.tw/auditionPersonal.html?gid=116\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tpe48.tw%2FauditionPersonal.html%3Fgid%3D116&d=7SLwcdWVY8Mpy4yKxH5Fd9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=107dfc1a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tpe48.tw/auditionPersonal.html?gid=116</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.likejapan.com/v2/d//2017/12/editors/9157/20171205171205_5a2662e5574a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.likejapan.com%2Fv2%2Fd%2F%2F2017%2F12%2Feditors%2F9157%2F20171205171205_5a2662e5574a0.jpg&h=504219f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNo.139 林裕君 官方簡介<a href=\"http://www.tpe48.tw/auditionPersonal.html?gid=139\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tpe48.tw%2FauditionPersonal.html%3Fgid%3D139&d=7SLwcdWVY8Mpy4yKxH5Fd9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=78e3655c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tpe48.tw/auditionPersonal.html?gid=139</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.likejapan.com/blogs/6%E5%90%8D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fblogs%2F6%25E5%2590%258D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258F%2583&d=7SLwcdWVY8Mpy4yKxH5Fd9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=7f73f6ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.likej